ai.grakn.migration.csv

Class CSVMigrator

  • java.lang.Object
    • ai.grakn.migration.csv.CSVMigrator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    public class CSVMigrator
extends Object
implements AutoCloseable
    The CSV migrator will migrate all of the data in a CSV file into Grakn Graql var patters, to be imported into a graph as the user sees fit.
    Author:
    alexandraorth
